.TH "nvme_init_get_log_sanitize" 9 "nvme_init_get_log_sanitize" "April 2026" "libnvme API manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
nvme_init_get_log_sanitize \- Initialize passthru command for Sanitize Status
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "void" nvme_init_get_log_sanitize
.BI "(struct libnvme_passthru_cmd *cmd "  ","
.BI "struct nvme_sanitize_log_page *log "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "cmd" 12
Passthru command to use
.IP "log" 12
User address to store the sanitize log
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Initializes the passthru command buffer for the Get Log command with
LID value NVME_LOG_LID_SANITIZE
